1.0.name: wordpress/gabeni
1.0.description:
Gabeni enables automated backups and 1 click restore of ANY wordpress installation. This is the only plugin that takes care of the retore process as well as the backup process.

The initial, free account, gives you 100MB of storage on our servers. You can keep only one backup file per domain and the plugin will not run automatic backups in the background. For $10 a year, you will have a consistent 200MB storage for your WordPress backups, automated backups that will run per schedule in the background and you will not be limited to 1 backup per domain.

  • No complicated setup
  • No technical knowledge required!
  • 100% safe backups!

So how does it work?

It's very easy.

When you download and enable the Gabeni plugin, you will be asked to enter your email address, first name and last name. Once you do that, the Gabeni plugin will automatically contact the Gabeni servers and create your account on th
